---
import Container from "../layouts/Container.astro";
---

<div class="full-screen">
  <Container>
    <section
      class="flex gap-20 justify-center flex-col-reverse md:flex-row md:justify-start"
    >
      <article class="flex flex-col justify-center md:justify-start items-center md:items-start gap-3">
        <p
          class="text-2xl md:text-5xl  text-center md:text-start text-[#171717] w-full md:w-[550px]"
        >
          Viaja a tu ritmo, sin prisa, sin estrés. Alquilando tu mejor vehículo.
        </p>
        <a class="w-[200px] px-5 py-3 bg-[#171717] hover:bg-[#252424] rounded-lg text-[#F8F8F9] cursor-pointer" href="/servicios">Comenzar reserva</a>
      </article>
      <article>
        <img src="auto2.webp" alt="logo auto banner" width="450px" />
      </article>
    </section>
  </Container>
</div>

<style>
  .full-screen {
    min-height: 85vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center; 
  }
</style>
